 \"highways\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 235}, {\"ngram\": \"jets\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 258}, {\"ngram\": \"the megaliths\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 276}, {\"ngram\": \"Stonehenge\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 290}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 309}, {\"ngram\": \"artworks\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 321}, {\"ngram\": \"some climate activists\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 345}, {\"ngram\": \"more provocative tactics\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 385}, {\"ngram\": \"the Covid-19\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 404}, {\"ngram\": \"an abrupt end\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 431}, {\"ngram\": \"the mass marches\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 451}, {\"ngram\": \"Future movement\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The last 12 months have been the hottest ever recorded and with swathes of the world blanketed in extreme heat, campaigners have heavy-polluting corporations and business interests in their sights.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 707, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The last 12 months\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 528}, {\"ngram\": \"swathes\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 581}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 594}, {\"ngram\": \"extreme heat\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 620}, {\"ngram\": \"campaigners\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 633}, {\"ngram\": \"heavy-polluting corporations\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"business interests\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"their sights\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A22 Network, an alliance of activist groups committed to non-violent protest, said it was planning to disrupt airports in eight countries over the northern hemisphere summer.\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 709, \"end\": 712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autostrade_of_Italy\", \"score\": 0.9999980151052713, \"rank\": 1.1931926016927902e-06, \"text\": \"A22\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Autostrade_of_Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://db