.9999088767996368, \"rank\": 9.104054630142228e-05, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}, {\"begin\": 1168, \"end\": 1174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8265184335941167, \"rank\": 0.20292934194662943, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Global aviation\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"around 2.5 per cent\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1087}, {\"ngram\": \"global carbon emissions\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"the annual carbon footprint\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our resistance will put the spotlight on the heaviest users of fossil fuels and call everyone into action with us,\\\" Just Stop Oil, one of the groups that embraced more controversial forms of protests, said in a statement.\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our resistance\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1201}, {\"ngram\": \"the spotlight\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \"the heaviest users\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"fossil fuels\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1262}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1280}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1292}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1300}, {\"ngram\": \"Oil\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"the groups\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1335}, {\"ngram\": \"more controversial forms\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"protests\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1386}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"UK police said they pre-emptively arrested 27 supporters from Just Stop Oil before the protest had even begun under laws that make it illegal to conspire to disrupt national infrastructure.\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1410, \"end\": 1412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.199269254187265e-12, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"27 supporters\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"Oil\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"the protest\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"laws\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"national infrastructure\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Gabriella Ditton, a spokesperson for the group, said the arrests had not deterred them.\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1605, \"end\": 1614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MS_Gabriella\", \"score\": 0.9994082953288825, \"rank\": 0.0005920535472797321, \"text\": \"Gabriella\", \"types\": [\"Q11446\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MS_Gabriella\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MS_Gabriella\"}, {\"begin\": 1615, \"end\": 1621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ditton_Priors\", \"score\": 0.9999999983110683, \"rank\": 9.017332113910305e-10, \"text\": \"Ditton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ditton_Priors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ditton_Priors\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a spokesperson\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1637}, {\"ngram\": \"the group\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1651}, {\"ngram\": \"the arrests\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1669}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEE ALSO \\\"While we face the massive crisis that we are in, we can not stop,\\\" she told AFP.\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1781, \"end\": 1784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999741130526, \"rank\": 2.5817850970441547e-08, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the massive crisis\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are demanding governments sign the Fossil Fuel Non-Proliferation Treaty Initiative, which seeks a halt to the expansion of fossil fuels and the phasing out of coal, oil and gas.\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"governments\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1817}, {\"ngram\": \"the Fossil Fuel Non-Proliferation Treaty Initiative\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1874}, {\"ngram\": \"a halt\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1894}, {\"ngram\": \"the expansion\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1911}, {\"ngram\": \"fossil fuels\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"the phasing\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1943}, {\"ngram\": \"coal\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1955}, {\"ngram\": \"oil\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1960}, {\"ngram\": \"gas\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the US, activists have been targeting Wall Street and barricading the entrances to major banks and firms that finance, insure and invest in fossil fuel companies.\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1978, \"end\": 1980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.6837754182515402, \"rank\": 0.46103800625373614, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"activists\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1991}, {\"ngram\": \"Wall Street\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2023}, {\"ngram\": \"the entrances\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\": \"major banks\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2068}, {\"ngram\": \"firms\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2078}, {\"ngram\": \"fossil fuel companies\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers of The Summer of Heat campaign have vowed \\\"joyful, relentless non-violent direct action to end fossil fuel financing\\\" over the coming months.\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2290, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organisers\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2148}, {\"ngram\": \"Heat\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"joyful, relentless non-violent direct action\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2236}, {\"ngram\": \"fossil fuel financing\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2265}, {\"ngram\": \"the coming months\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2289}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Notably in Europe, Extinction Rebellion (XR), once notorious for shutting down bridges over the Thames River in London, have shifted their main focus from mass civil disobedience to building an inclusive grassroots movement.\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2404, \"end\": 2410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999524793577, \"rank\": 4.7084856408016685e-08, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2309}, {\"ngram\": \"Extinction Rebellion\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"XR\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2335}, {\"ngram\": \"bridges\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"the Thames River\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2400}, {\"ngram\": \"their main focus\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2441}, {\"ngram\": \"mass civil disobedience\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2470}, {\"ngram\": \"an inclusive grassroots movement\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This summer, they are calling on governments in the UK and France to establish citizen assemblies on climate and nature, while picketing the companies insuring the fossil fuel industry.\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2570, \"end\": 2572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 7.199269254187265e-12, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2577, \"end\": 2583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8265184335941167, \"rank\": 0.20292934194662943, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"governments\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2562}, {\"ngram\": \"citizen assemblies\", \"from\": 2597, \"to\": 2615}, {\"ngram\": \"climate\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2626}, {\"ngram\": \"nature\", \"from\": 2631, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"the companies\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2668}, {\"ngram\": \"the fossil fuel industry\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gail Bradbrook, XR's co-founder, told AFP their new-look approach to climate activism strived \\\"to reach more mainstream folks\\\" and do \\\"the deeper work of local organising\\\".\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2705, \"end\": 2719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gail_Bradbrook\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gail Bradbrook\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gail_Bradbrook\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gail_Bradbrook\"}, {\"begin\": 2721, \"end\": 2723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Extinction_Rebellion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.549351529800084e-54, \"text\": \"XR\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.or